-- U.S. Issues Travel Alert for Americans in Europe, Citing Terrorism Threat
-- B y   A n n   H u g h e y
-- 2010-10-03T12:46:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-03/u-s-issues-travel-alert-for-americans-in-europe-citing-terrorism-threat.html
The U.S. State Department issued an
alert warning U.S. citizens to “the potential for terrorist
attacks in Europe.”  “Current information suggests that al-Qaeda and affiliated
organizations continue to plan terrorist attacks,” the
department said in a statement. “U.S. citizens are reminded of
the potential for terrorists to attack public transportation
systems and other tourist infrastructure.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ann Hughey at 
 ahughey@bloomberg.net  